<L>__{interior halls of barbara bush high school day}
<A>__{marianne, angry as hell, stomps through the hall with hatred burning in her eyes and coursing through her veins.}
<C>__{olive }
<D>__{but then i unwittingly gave her boyfriend a venerial disease...}
<A>__{marianne stops in front of olive and slaps her so hard that people in the hallways stop, dead in their tracks. it's the slap heard `round the school.}
<L>__{interior guidance office day}
<A>__{olive bursts into mrs. griffin's office. tear streaked, mrs. griffin is packing her things into a cardboard box. it's as if her world has just collapsed.}
<C>__{olive }
<D>__{...and caused the break up of mr. and mrs. griffin...}
<C>__{mrs. griffin}
<P>__{(snapping)}
<D>__{what?! what do you want?}
<A>__{olive starts to say something, but mrs. griffin can't even look at her.}
<C>__{mrs. griffin }
<D>__{just go!}
<A>__{she throws a framed photo of her and mr. griffin into the box. it shatters. mrs. griffin falls apart. olive starts to say something again, but she doesn't know what to say, so she sheepishly turns to leave.}
